{"tid":1574290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門候任特首賀一誠稱不能不講一國只講兩制，要在中央政府的領導下，堅定不移貫徹落實 一國兩制方針","createTime":"2019-09-16T10:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T10:55:04.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7b92095714cbee3e75ec776e36fe138b5eb7ed","tid":1574290,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1592389/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%AC%9B%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%AA%E8%AC%9B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1592389%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2580%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25B3%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AC%259B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=8572b2e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1592389%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2580%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25B3%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AC%259B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6&h=dd773025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1592389/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%AC%9B%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%AA%E8%AC%9B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n即時新聞港聞選擇分類 <br />\n澳門候任特首賀一誠稱不能不講一國只講兩制<br />\n2019-09-16 14:59 文字大小<br />\n賀一誠訪問中央廣播電視總台並接受訪問。網上圖片<br />\n賀一誠訪問中央廣播電視總台並接受訪問。網上圖片<br />\n澳門候任行政長官賀一誠訪問中央廣播電視總台，與中宣部副部長、中央廣播電視總台台長慎海雄會面，並接受訪問。談到如何踐行一國兩制，賀一誠強調，一定要先奠定好一國的概念，不能不講一國，只講兩制。在一國的前提，要知道哪些是國家的底線不能碰、不能走樣，當澳門做好兩制的制度，才能保持一國兩制行穩致遠。<br />\n<br />\n賀一誠稱，要在中央政府的領導下，堅定不移貫徹落實 一國兩制方針，推進一國兩制在澳門的實踐行穩致遠。要維護好憲法和基本法權威，維護好內地與澳門的良好關係，維護好中央的全面管治權，維護好國家主權、安全和發展利益。"},{"pid":"5e291c2b7a0111db1f4e3ac8546182ddf8da1bb6","tid":1574290,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=50ee127c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=8865ef14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"d386427f356265b476cc3db8cb26dd45e2b6efa3","tid":1574290,"uid":63757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"死太監<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25af0399d65c1e487bc365c8447b22ddaa2e21c","tid":1574290,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s